trans-unit.source: Get Metadata Document
trans-unit.target: Get Metadata Document

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>Get Metadata Document</languageKeyword> operation retrieves the service metadata document, which describes the complete data model for the resources exposed by the Windows Azure Import/Export service.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>Get Metadata Document</languageKeyword> operation retrieves the service metadata document, which describes the complete data model for the resources exposed by the Windows Azure Import/Export service.

trans-unit.source: The service metadata document is defined by the OData Protocol.
trans-unit.target: The service metadata document is defined by the OData Protocol.

trans-unit.source: The service metadata document provides the entity data type information that is needed when constructing certain requests against the Import/Export service.
trans-unit.target: The service metadata document provides the entity data type information that is needed when constructing certain requests against the Import/Export service.

trans-unit.source: It is also needed to correctly parse responses from the Import/Export service.
trans-unit.target: It is also needed to correctly parse responses from the Import/Export service.
